## 1. ArmEnvironment.cs — Fix IL2026/IL3050 on line 80

Line 80: `public override string ToString() => JsonSerializer.Serialize(this);`

The `ArmEnvironment` struct has properties `Endpoint` (Uri) and `Audience` (string) and `DefaultScope` (string).

Replace the JsonSerializer.Serialize call with manual JSON construction:
```csharp
public override string ToString()
